scene.message:
Mark: This kid! Isn't she{nl}
the ghost from the museum?{nl}
One of that brat's friends?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: So that's the key{nl}
to the castle... But who{nl}
on earth are these children?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Hey, Mai-chan,{nl}
you know a girl named "Aki,"{nl}
right? Is she your friend?{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: No she's not!{nl}
She's not my friend at all!{nl}
She's a Mai-chan too...{waitkey}{clearbox}A bad Mai-chan...{nl}
Waaaaaaaaaah!!{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: Sob... Mai-chan{nl}
was so lonely...{nl}
then Kandori came...{waitkey}{clearbox}And then she came out{nl}
of Mai-chan and went{nl}
off with Kandori...{waitkey}{clearbox}Even though she knows{nl}
Kandori isn't papa...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A separate self split{nl}
from one person, I see...{nl}
What is that compact?{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: It's Mai-chan's{nl}
treasure... it grants{nl}
any wish.{waitkey}Mai-chan made this whole{nl}
town with it.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It can't be...{nl}
that such a tiny child is{nl}
this world's Creator...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Awesome~!{nl}
She's like a little witch!{nl}
I want one of those.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Using that compact,{nl}
could you catch Aki and{nl}
Kandori, or send everyone{waitkey}back to their world somehow?{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: I can't...{nl}
Aki took half of it{nl}
away from me...{waitkey}{clearbox}I know Aki uses her half{nl}
to do bad things, but my{nl}
wishes get cancelled out.{waitkey}{clearbox}So I'm hiding here.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: But without it,{nl}
we can't reach Kandori.{nl}
Could you lend it a sec?{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: No way!{nl}
This is the very thing{nl}
Kandori wants!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: That's right.{nl}
{ctl07:1} is right.{nl}
Running solves nothing.{waitkey}You have to fight!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Honestly, {ctl07:1}!{nl}
Don't joke around.{nl}
Running solves nothing.{waitkey}That's why you fight.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Argh!{nl}
No time to dawdle! We've{nl}
gotta get back fast{waitkey}{clearbox}- there's someone we have{nl}
to save! Please! Lend it{nl}
to us!{waitkey}The way she looked, she's...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: D-don't be stupid!{nl}
She's definitely alive!{nl}
Anyway, look...{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: Mister, all of you...{nl}
why do you live?{nl}
Isn't living... painful?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...That's true.{nl}
{ctl07:1} is right.{nl}
Besides, if you're alive,{waitkey}there are joys to be had.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: ...Yeah, that's it!{nl}
{ctl08:6401}He's right.{nl}
If you live, there's fun{waitkey}to be had too.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...Yeah,{nl}
{ctl0f:1} might be right.{nl}
Live, and there's fun too.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It's been a while{nl}
since I thought about this...{nl}
but there are joys, too...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Been a while since{nl}
I thought about stuff like{nl}
this... but there's fun too...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: It's been a while{nl}
since I thought about this...{nl}
there's fun too, but...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1} is right.{nl}
Live, and good things{nl}
happen too.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: How unreliable...{nl}
Well, it's a hard question,{nl}
but live and good comes too.{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: I see...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
Mai-chan will stay here{nl}
after all. I can't lend{waitkey}the compact. I'm sorry.{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: Sniff...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
No way!{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Nomoraka Tanomama!{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: I see...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
If it's you, mister...{nl}
I'll lend you the compact.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Alright!{nl}
Thanks, Mai-chan!{waitkey}Let's make a wish and have{nl}
it carry us to Kandori!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Thanks!{nl}
Let's wish at once and have{nl}
it carry us to Kandori.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Fools.{nl}
This is no time for greed.{nl}
Have it take us to Kandori.{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: It's no good.{nl}
Only Mai-chan can{nl}
use it.{waitkey}{clearbox}And the castle is Aki's{nl}
house, so it won't grant{nl}
Mai-chan's wishes there.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: No way!{nl}
And I had so many wishes~{nl}
The worst!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1},{nl}
show me that compact.{waitkey}{clearbox}Huh - it's only half, but{nl}
it's the same as mine...{waitkey}Mine has no mirror, but{nl}
this one's still got it.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Well, wishes are{nl}
something you make come{nl}
true yourself.{waitkey}If everything went your way,{nl}
the world'd be boring.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That Kandori...{nl}
What does he mean to do{nl}
once he has the compact...?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: When I was little, I'd{nl}
pretend the mirror at home{nl}
was a magic mirror and wish.{waitkey}{clearbox}"Let me become a pretty{nl}
girl everyone likes"...{nl}
something like that...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Aww~{nl}
I've got so many things I{nl}
want! {ctl0f:1}, buy 'em? Hm?{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: Please don't let{nl}
Kandori take the{nl}
compact.
